<item>
            <title>[LU-5027] Needs rhel 6.5 support in b2_4</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5027</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A few weeks ago one of the LU&apos;s I am following was closed with a patch.&lt;br/&gt;
(I do not remember which one. )&lt;br/&gt;
The patch was landed to b2_5 only. When I tried to back port it to b2_4,&lt;br/&gt;
it failed because the patch had a dependency of changes in rhel 6.5.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I noticed rhel 6.5 has been supported in lustre 2.5.1. Please also&lt;br/&gt;
support rhel 6.5 in b2_4.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
