                            <comment id="83622" author="pjones" created="Fri, 9 May 2014 14:22:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My understanding from yesterday&apos;s call is that NASA plans to move forward with the back port of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4791&quot; title=&quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4791&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4791&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for now&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="83520" author="bogl" created="Thu, 8 May 2014 15:20:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;back port of the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4791&quot; title=&quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4791&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4791&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix to b2_4 is in progress: &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/10267&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/10267&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="83465" author="jaylan" created="Wed, 7 May 2014 23:06:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mahmoud filed &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4623&quot; title=&quot;creating file stripe &amp;gt; 167 fails &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4623&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4623&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &quot;creating file stripe &amp;gt; 167 fails&quot;. The ticket was closed&lt;br/&gt;
as a duplicate to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4260&quot; title=&quot;ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4260&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4260&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &quot;ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4791&quot; title=&quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4791&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4791&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed&quot; was&lt;br/&gt;
fixed with a different patch. Di Wang commented at 18/Apr/14 7:16 PM that&lt;br/&gt;
I needed both patches from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4260&quot; title=&quot;ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4260&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4260&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4791&quot; title=&quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4791&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4791&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So I cherry-picked &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4791&quot; title=&quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4791&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4791&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; patch to our nas-2.4.3. The compilation failed&lt;br/&gt;
in our rhel 6.4 environment because some changes in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4791&quot; title=&quot;lod_ah_init() ASSERTION( lc-&amp;gt;ldo_stripenr == 0 ) failed:&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4791&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4791&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; had a dependency&lt;br/&gt;
on rhel 6.5 (changes in ext4 area.)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="83463" author="pjones" created="Wed, 7 May 2014 22:44:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Jay&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let&apos;s discuss the options on tomorrow&apos;s call&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Peter&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
